sd=Position Keeping	This service domain maintains a financial transaction log to support production. Reconciled financial transactions are subsequently posted to the accounting systems	"Any product fulfillment domain, current account, savings account, credit card, etc, delegates transaction posting/track to the Position Keeping service domain."	Maintain a log of financial transactions for management information, tracking and reconciliation purposes.  It can offer utilities that enable it to maintain balances/positions, to calculate interest and to support transaction reconciliation activities The financial transactions are subsequently posted to the accounting systems
sdpath=position-keeping
crpath=financial-position-log
crr=Financial Position Log Instance
mcr=Financial Position Log
bqs=Transaction Capture
CONFIG
FinancialPositionLog	initiate	Initiate a position keeping transaction log		initiateFinancialPositionLog		#desc
FinancialPositionLog	update	Update details for an active financial transaction log, including reflecting an account block (this is managed by the fulfillment SD)		updateFinancialPositionLog		#desc
FinancialPositionLog	control	Control the processing of the log (e.g. suspend)		controlFinancialPositionLog		#desc
FinancialPositionLog	retrieve	Retrieve information about the log		retrieveFinancialPositionLog		#desc
TransactionCapture	update	Update details of a captured financial transaction	updateFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture	updateFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture		Update to any amendable fields of the Transaction Capture instance
TransactionCapture	capture	Capture details of a financial transaction in the log	captureFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture	captureFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture		Provide a structured input transaction/record (e.g. timesheet, event)
TransactionCapture	retrieve	Retrieve details of financial transactions captured in the log	retrieveFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture	retrieveFinancialPositionLogTransactionCapture		Invoke a reporting action to obtain a Transaction Capture instance related report